The Bill Douglas Trilogy(1972-78)<br/>
Its as great as Eisenstein.Crispand somber, but ayoung manemerges.<br/>
<br/>
Theorem (1968)<br/>
Queerness as a crowbar, to force open the cracks in polite society. Funny,too.</p></div>

<h3 aria-label="" class="Headline__H3-sc-e1fxl5-3 fnpSex">Alex Davidson, Writer and Programmer, <span class="caps">BFI</span></h3>

